headline: Waters Corporation to Present at the Jefferies Global Healthcare Conference
summary: Waters Corporation (NYSE:WAT) announced that Udit Batra, Ph.D., Waters President and Chief Executive Officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the Jefferies Global Healthcare Conference on Wednesday, June 4th, 2025, at 8:45AM Eastern Time.
